# Cloudflare Pages runs `npm clean-install` when a lockfile exists, which then
# breaks the `npx @cloudflare/next-on-pages` peer resolution (wrangler vs
# @cloudflare/workers-types). Stay lockfile-less so the deploy uses `npm install`.
package-lock.json
